OL,3,CNepal bus crash: Tributes to Briton
OL,4,Cwho was among the 19 killed
OL,6,FA 23-year-old British man is among 19
OL,7,Fpeople who were killed in a bus crash
OL,8,Fin Nepal, police have said.
OL,10,FThe bus, which had been carrying
OL,11,Ftourists, had been travelling to the
OL,12,Fcapital, Kathmandu, when it lost
OL,13,Fcontrol and fell 200m onto the bank of
OL,14,Fthe Trishuli river. 44 people were on
OL,15,Fboard, 25 of whom suffered injuries.
OL,17,FDominic Stewart, 23, had just
OL,18,Fcompleted the Annapurma Circut, which
OL,19,Fis a popular hiking route in Nepal,
OL,20,Fbefore the crash. He was due celebrate
OL,21,Fhis 24th birthday in March.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
