PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772012410
OL,3,CNepal bus crash: Tributes to Briton
OL,4,Cwho was among the 19 killed
OL,6,FHis family has now paid tribute to a
OL,7,F"very loving and caring young man who
OL,8,Fwas happiest trekking".
OL,10,FHis father said he had lived his whole
OL,11,Flife in Exeter and was well known in
OL,12,Fjunior football.
OL,14,FDominic's name has not been confirmed
OL,15,Fby the Foreign Office but in a
OL,16,Fstatement a spokesperson said: "We are
OL,17,Fsupporting the family of a British man
OL,18,Fwho has died in Nepal and are in
OL,19,Fcontact with the local authorities".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/2
